#: incl/pages/main.php:22
msgid ""
"You can control who can use each block, including default WordPress blocks."
msgstr ""
"Anda dapat mengontrol siapa yang dapat menggunakan masing - masing blok, "
"termasuk blok standar WordPress."

#: incl/pages/main.php:32
msgid ""
"Enable extra blocks including content displays, sliders, buttons, icons, "
"tabs, accordions, and more."
msgstr ""
"Aktifkan blok ekstra termasuk tampilan konten, slider, tombol, ikon, "
"tabulasi, accordion, dan lain sebagainya."

